JBoss AS 7 Webservice Example
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Build the example with maven 
	
	mvn clean package
	
2. Deploy  the webservice 
	cp /webservice-example/webservice-example-ejb/target/webservice-example-ejb-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar $JBOSS_HOME/standalone/deployments
	
3. Execute the Example Client Application 
	webservice-example-client
	
4. Deploy the EJB Client Example	
	cp /webservice-example/webservice-example-ear/target/webservice-example-ear $JBOSS_HOME/standalone/deployments
	
5. 	Navigate to http://localhost:8080/webservice-example